Description: This package implements Multivariate Adaptive Regression 
          Splines (MARS), a versatile and interpretable regression modeling 
          technique. MARS captures complex nonlinear relationships using 
          piecewise linear functions, making it suitable for various applications
          such as predictive modeling and data analysis. With 'mars', users can fit
          MARS models, perform model selection, visualize results, interpret output, and predict future values.
